Text: Restructuring Conference PublicityJeff We have very strong registrations for the Energy Restructuring in California conference and will have a very interesting audience in addition to our excellent faculty Here is an easy way to let your clients colleagues and associates know about the conference and your role as a member of the faculty Simply delete the first part of this email message and forward the remainder to the people of your choice Feel free to edit the message This is a service we offer to faculty members who want to help publicize the conference It is not a requirement Best regards Karl Craine Executive Director This is just a short note to let you know that I will be speaking at Energy Restructuring in California conference that will take place on November and in San Francisco It should be an excellent program for anyone dealing with dealing with Californias transition to competitive energy markets For more information follow this link htmlsseminarsresca You also can call Law Seminars International at or
